<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='758891' id='t-758891'>from this treatment.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='760758' id='t-760758'>And if that's the case,
that could give us hope</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='763338' id='t-763338'>that what I showed you works in mice</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='765782' id='t-765782'>might also work in humans.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
12:59
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='768478' id='t-768478'>Now, I don't think we will live forever.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='771955' id='t-771955'>But maybe we discovered</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='774316' id='t-774316'>that the Fountain of Youth
is actually within us,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='777427' id='t-777427'>and it has just dried out.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='779574' id='t-779574'>And if we can turn it
