<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='793725' id='t-793725'>or other dementias.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
13:26
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='795282' id='t-795282'>Thank you very much.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
13:27
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
